{
          "cells": [
                    {
                              "cell_type": "markdown",
                              "id": "93c97ba6",
                              "metadata": {},
                              "source": [
                                        "# DQ Suite Runner\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "Runs all data quality contracts for a **project workspace** and persists results\n",
                                        "to the central **DQ engine workspace**.\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "### Workspace variables\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "| Variable | Purpose |\n",
                                        "|---|---|\n",
                                        "| `CONTRACT_WORKSPACE_NAME` | Workspace that holds the YAML contract / suite files |\n",
                                        "| `DATA_WORKSPACE_NAME` | Workspace that contains the actual data tables (can differ from contracts) |\n",
                                        "| `DQ_RESULTS_WORKSPACE_NAME` | Workspace where scan results are persisted (central DQ engine) |\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "Set any of these to `None` to fall back to the current (auto-detected) workspace.\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "### Steps\n",
                                        "1. Configure the cell below.\n",
                                        "2. Run all cells — contracts are discovered automatically or filtered by suite.\n",
                                        "3. Results are displayed inline and written to Delta tables in the results workspace.\n"
                              ]
                    },
                    {
                              "cell_type": "markdown",
                              "id": "59b44812",
                              "metadata": {},
                              "source": [
                                        "## 1 Â· Configuration"
                              ]
                    },
                    {
                              "cell_type": "code",
                              "execution_count": null,
                              "id": "85fc1f58",
                              "metadata": {},
                              "outputs": [],
                              "source": [
                                        "import os\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# ── Contracts workspace ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
                                        "# Workspace that holds the contract / suite YAML files.\n",
                                        "# Set to None to auto-detect (current notebook workspace).\n",
                                        "CONTRACT_WORKSPACE_NAME: str | None = None\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# Lakehouse inside that workspace whose Files/dataquality/contracts/ folder holds YAMLs.\n",
                                        "CONTRACT_LAKEHOUSE_NAME: str = \"bronze\"\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# Sub-folder inside Files/ where contracts live.\n",
                                        "CONTRACTS_FOLDER: str = \\"dataquality/contracts\\"\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# Sub-folder inside Files/ where suite files live.\n",
                                        "SUITES_FOLDER: str = \"suites\"\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# Name of the suite to run (without .yaml). Set to None to run all contracts.\n",
                                        "SUITE_NAME: str | None = None  # e.g. \"daily_critical\"\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# ── Data workspace ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
                                        "# Workspace that contains the actual Delta/Parquet data tables.\n",
                                        "# Set to None when contracts and data live in the same workspace.\n",
                                        "DATA_WORKSPACE_NAME: str | None = None\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# ── DQ results workspace ───────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
                                        "# Workspace where scan results are persisted (central DQ engine workspace).\n",
                                        "# Set to None to write results into the contract workspace instead.\n",
                                        "# Typically injected as a Fabric Environment variable per environment.\n",
                                        "DQ_RESULTS_WORKSPACE_NAME: str | None = os.environ.get(\"DQ_RESULTS_WORKSPACE_NAME\") or None\n",
                                        "DQ_RESULTS_LAKEHOUSE_NAME: str = os.environ.get(\"DQ_RESULTS_LAKEHOUSE_NAME\") or \"gold\"\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# ── Runtime variable overrides ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
                                        "# Applied to every contract's ${VAR} placeholders.\n",
                                        "RUNTIME_VARIABLES: dict = {\n",
                                        "    # \"FILTER_START_TIME\": \"2024-01-01 00:00:00\",\n",
                                        "}\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# ── Row flagging & remediation ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
                                        "FLAG_ROWS: bool = True       # add _dq_failed / _dq_failed_checks columns\n",
                                        "APPLY_ACTIONS: bool = False  # apply on_fail remediation actions\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "# ── Persistence options ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
                                        "PERSIST_RESULTS: bool = True\n",
                                        "PERSIST_FLAGGED_ROWS: bool = True   # requires FLAG_ROWS = True\n",
                                        "PERSIST_QUARANTINED: bool = True    # requires APPLY_ACTIONS = True\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "print(\"Configuration loaded.\")\n",
                                        "print(f\"  contracts workspace : {CONTRACT_WORKSPACE_NAME or '(auto-detect)'}\")\n",
                                        "print(f\"  data workspace      : {DATA_WORKSPACE_NAME or '(same as contracts)'}\")\n",
                                        "print(f\"  results workspace   : {DQ_RESULTS_WORKSPACE_NAME or '(same as contracts)'}\")\n",
                                        "print(f\"  suite               : {SUITE_NAME or '(all contracts)'}\")\n"
                              ]
                    },
                    {
                              "cell_type": "markdown",
                              "id": "08205d3d",
                              "metadata": {},
                              "source": [
                                        "## 2 · Load suite / discover contracts"
                              ]
                    },
                    {
                              "cell_type": "code",
                              "execution_count": null,
                              "id": "a04a72dc",
                              "metadata": {},
                              "outputs": [],
                              "source": [
                                        "from ouroboros_gx import discover_contracts, discover_suites, load_suite\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "if SUITE_NAME:\n",
                                        "    print(f\"Loading suite: {SUITE_NAME}\")\n",
                                        "    contract_urls = load_suite(\n",
                                        "        contract_workspace_name=CONTRACT_WORKSPACE_NAME,\n",
                                        "        lakehouse_name=CONTRACT_LAKEHOUSE_NAME,\n",
                                        "        suite_name=SUITE_NAME,\n",
                                        "        contracts_folder=CONTRACTS_FOLDER,\n",
                                        "        suites_folder=SUITES_FOLDER,\n",
                                        "    )\n",
                                        "else:\n",
                                        "    print(\"No suite selected — discovering all contracts.\")\n",
                                        "    available_suites = discover_suites(\n",
                                        "        contract_workspace_name=CONTRACT_WORKSPACE_NAME,\n",
                                        "        lakehouse_name=CONTRACT_LAKEHOUSE_NAME,\n",
                                        "        suites_folder=SUITES_FOLDER,\n",
                                        "    )\n",
                                        "    if available_suites:\n",
                                        "        print(f\"Available suites: {available_suites}\")\n",
                                        "        contract_urls = discover_contracts(\n",
                                        "            contract_workspace_name=CONTRACT_WORKSPACE_NAME,\n",
                                        "            lakehouse_name=CONTRACT_LAKEHOUSE_NAME,\n",
                                        "            folder=CONTRACTS_FOLDER,\n",
                                        "        )\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "print(f\"\\nContracts to run ({len(contract_urls)}):\")\n",
                                        "for url in contract_urls:\n",
                                        "    print(f\"  {url.split('/')[-1]}\")\n"
                              ]
                    },
                    {
                              "cell_type": "markdown",
                              "id": "f05d4944",
                              "metadata": {},
                              "source": [
                                        "## 4 Â· Run contracts & persist results"
                              ]
                    },
                    {
                              "cell_type": "code",
                              "execution_count": null,
                              "id": "d8d63d67",
                              "metadata": {},
                              "outputs": [],
                              "source": [
                                        "from ouroboros_gx import DQRunner, persist_results\n",
                                        "from ouroboros_gx.result_reporter import display_results, summarize\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "all_summaries = []\n",
                                        "run_ids = {}\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "for contract_url in contract_urls:\n",
                                        "    dataset_name = contract_url.split(\"/\")[-1].replace(\".yaml\", \"\").replace(\".yml\", \"\")\n",
                                        "    print(f\"\\n{'─' * 60}\")\n",
                                        "    print(f\"Running: {dataset_name}\")\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "    try:\n",
                                        "        runner = DQRunner(\n",
                                        "            contract_url,\n",
                                        "            variables=RUNTIME_VARIABLES,\n",
                                        "            data_workspace_name=DATA_WORKSPACE_NAME or CONTRACT_WORKSPACE_NAME,\n",
                                        "        )\n",
                                        "        result = runner.run(\n",
                                        "            flag_rows=FLAG_ROWS,\n",
                                        "            apply_actions=APPLY_ACTIONS,\n",
                                        "        )\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "        display_results(result)\n",
                                        "        summary = summarize(result)\n",
                                        "        all_summaries.append(summary)\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "        if PERSIST_RESULTS:\n",
                                        "            run_id = persist_results(\n",
                                        "                result,\n",
                                        "                dq_workspace_name=DQ_RESULTS_WORKSPACE_NAME or CONTRACT_WORKSPACE_NAME,\n",
                                        "                lakehouse_name=DQ_RESULTS_LAKEHOUSE_NAME,\n",
                                        "                data_workspace_name=DATA_WORKSPACE_NAME or CONTRACT_WORKSPACE_NAME,\n",
                                        "                data_lakehouse_name=CONTRACT_LAKEHOUSE_NAME,\n",
                                        "                persist_flagged_rows=PERSIST_FLAGGED_ROWS and FLAG_ROWS,\n",
                                        "                persist_quarantined=PERSIST_QUARANTINED and APPLY_ACTIONS,\n",
                                        "                dataset_source=runner.contract.source,\n",
                                        "            )\n",
                                        "            run_ids[dataset_name] = run_id\n",
                                        "            print(f\"  ✅ Persisted — run_id: {run_id}\")\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "    except Exception as exc:\n",
                                        "        print(f\"  ❌ ERROR running contract '{dataset_name}': {exc}\")\n",
                                        "        all_summaries.append({\n",
                                        "            \"dataset\": dataset_name,\n",
                                        "            \"total_checks\": 0,\n",
                                        "            \"passed\": 0,\n",
                                        "            \"failed\": 1,\n",
                                        "            \"warnings\": 0,\n",
                                        "            \"success_rate_pct\": 0.0,\n",
                                        "            \"overall_success\": False,\n",
                                        "        })\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "print(f\"\\n{'═' * 60}\")\n",
                                        "print(f\"Suite complete — {len(contract_urls)} contract(s) processed.\")\n"
                              ]
                    },
                    {
                              "cell_type": "markdown",
                              "id": "515ba98d",
                              "metadata": {},
                              "source": [
                                        "## 5 Â· Batch summary"
                              ]
                    },
                    {
                              "cell_type": "code",
                              "execution_count": null,
                              "id": "d7ca3baf",
                              "metadata": {},
                              "outputs": [],
                              "source": [
                                        "import pandas as pd\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "summary_df = pd.DataFrame(all_summaries)\n",
                                        "if not summary_df.empty:\n",
                                        "    summary_df = summary_df.sort_values(\"overall_success\")\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "    def _style(row):\n",
                                        "        color = \"#d4edda\" if row[\"overall_success\"] else \"#f8d7da\"\n",
                                        "        return [f\"background-color: {color}\"] * len(row)\n",
                                        "\n",
                                        "    display(summary_df.style.apply(_style, axis=1))\n",
                                        "else:\n",
                                        "    print(\"No contracts were run.\")"
                              ]
                    }
          ],
          "metadata": {
                    "language_info": {
                              "name": "python"
                    }
          },
          "nbformat": 4,
          "nbformat_minor": 5
}
